cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper deals with algorithms for empirical policy evaluation in reinforcement learning, which is a problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves exploration and analysis of algorithms, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The problem of reinforcement learning is related to control systems, which could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper deals with optimization of sample complexity, which could be related to cs.RO (Robotics).
